# Backend handoff

Backend work starts after frontend compilation. The frontend hands over validated HIR, the paired `TypeEnvironment`, borrow facts and builder-facing metadata. Project builders assemble artifacts and backend lowerers emit target-specific code.

## Category contract

- The build system owns orchestration and output writing.
- Project builders own project-specific artifact assembly.
- Backend lowerers own target-specific code generation from validated HIR and companion metadata.

