## Category-wide invariants

- The HTML project builder applies one shared fragment plan around either selected execution path.
- JavaScript and Wasm lowerers provide target execution artifacts. They don't own page-fragment ordering.
- Backend validation evaluates the selected target contract through explicit reachability root policies.
